-- 2010-11-10T17:03:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-10/u-s-debt-commission-s-chairmen-to-release-plan-for-reducing-deficit-today.html
Erskine Bowles and Alan Simpson, the
co-chairmen of the U.S. debt-reduction commission, plan to
release their proposal to the panel today at 1 p.m. Washington
time, said a spokesman, Fred Baldassaro.  To contact the reporter on this story:
